config TRINITY_MODE_BENCH
    bool "Trinity bench mode — halt on crash for USB-JTAG attach"
    default n
    help
      When enabled, panic handler halts in an infinite loop.
      Attach ESP32-C3 USB-JTAG debugger to inspect state.
      Use this mode on the dev bench only.

config TRINITY_MODE_USB
    bool "Trinity USB mode — USB CDC log transport + restart"
    default n
    help
      When enabled, console output goes to USB CDC serial.
      Panic handler logs to NVS and calls esp_restart().
      Use when device is USB-tethered for field testing.
